melding: Skiene var så lange at de knakk i første sving! Dårlig ass, hadde fått mye bedre ski i nærmeste sportsbutikk!
that stupid rocket didn't work. yes very bad i paid very many money for it. now my country's treasury is empty again. i demand a refund so that i can buy another rocket
my son used our whole treasury on your stupid rockets. i never gave him permission to use my credit card i need a refund, daddy wanna build another statue of himself
Jeg sa at jeg skulle laste ned appen hvis han lagde den ferdig uten bugs, men han har aldri gjort. Venter ennå på heismusikke HANS!!!
